\c 3
\rem Front matter For the Epistle of James
\imt Ulutango ulwa kiyimba gina gayandiikhwe mu litaafili ili
\ip Pawutasi iMola iNofu yayandiikhwe kwa Shiyunaani. Kihuma pina yayandiikhwe, yiganwilwe mu filogolo finshi. Hata ilitaafili ili, liganwilwe kihuma mu shilogolo sha Shiyunaani. Baheene khanji lyaganulwagwa mu shilogolo sha Shingelesa ni Shiswahili.
\is1 1. Uwuganulaaji wa Maswi aMahensa
\ip Mu Mayandikhwa aManofu gakwali amaswi aganji gina mahensa mu shilogolo sha Shisangu. Amaswi ago gakwali kuwutasi wa litaafili ili, uluvala ulwa wuganulaaji wa Maswi aMahensa. Nda kuna liswi likhamu mu litaafili, tikiliwonensa mu futinoti kiija ukwiliile kilipata mu Maswi aMahensa.
\is1 2. Ifutinoti
\ip Ifutinoti siganula pansi pa wukulaasa (Yaakobo 1:25), khanji siwonensa uluvala luna ukwiliile kipata pina yiyandiikhwe mu mataafili aganji (Yaakobo 2:8).
\is1 3. Ifipuga mu mayandikhwa ga litaafili ili
\ip Mu mayandikhwa ago gavishiilwe fipuga fipuga, kwa kiiva ya mola iya shipuga isho. Ifipuga ifi fisivishiilwe mu mayandikhwa amakuulu aga Shiyunaani. Leelo aMayandikhwa aManofu aga luhaavi ulu, gana fipuga.
